{"tid":823783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[屌你老母] 交通癱瘓 上水及大埔墟站千人排隊","createTime":"2018-09-17T01:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T01:09:43.000Z","uid":170646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13762bb5641ddcf6d3d51fe085a2ae7179fdbbbc","tid":823783,"uid":170646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:04:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【交通癱瘓】上水及大埔墟站千人排隊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n東鐵部份路線暫停服務，估計修復時間需要4小時，巴士服務則大部份受影響，今早約7時，在上水火車站，已約有一千人排隊等候港駁巴士出市區，惟港鐵接駁巴士不是，未有足夠車輛及時疏導乘客，接駁巴士站無車，卻有大量乘客在等候，秩序良好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180917/58690340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58690340&d=jswbPQnabvIpAkxVJWlMC54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ced12b54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58690340&h=6429ead6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180917/58690340</a><br />\n<br />\n我以為打完十號風球零死亡已經好癲<br />\n點知第二日仲要人番工呢下仲癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母政府"},{"pid":"fe7478fa56c3834ef682bdd3124d1080859a1077","tid":823783,"uid":170646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:06:27.000Z","msg":"[無車點撚樣番工] 新界北交通討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/823451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/823451</a>"},{"pid":"d7ba13be53390406fdf9ad910f297e23dbe3ce25","tid":823783,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:08:12.000Z","msg":"港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f9cb3af982d913b64455f853f05f44efbb71d8","tid":823783,"uid":170646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upl